flowchart TD
    A[Queued ingestion_job] --> B[Worker loads job by job_id]
    B --> C[Load document by project_id + document_id]
    C --> D[Mark job running and document processing]
    D --> E{Select parser by file type}

    E -->|PDF| P[PyMuPDF parser]
    E -->|DOCX| X[python-docx parser]
    E -->|TXT| T[TXT parser]
    E -->|XLSX| S[openpyxl parser]

    P --> N[Normalized sections]
    X --> N
    T --> N
    S --> N

    N --> H[Generate chunk candidates]
    H --> I[Compute content hashes]
    I --> J[Call embedding provider]
    J --> K{Validate embeddings}

    K -->|valid| L[Replace sections and chunks in DB]
    L --> M[DB trigger updates search_vector]
    M --> O[Mark job completed and document indexed]

    K -->|invalid| F[Mark job failed]
    E -->|unsupported| F
    N -->|no usable text| F
    J -->|API error| F
    L -->|DB error| F

    F --> G[Store error_message]
    G --> R[Document leaves processing state]

    subgraph Safety[Reindex Safety]
        Old[Existing indexed chunks]
        New[New parse/chunk/embed result]
        Old -->|preserve until new result succeeds| New
    end
